OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776682974
OL,3,CFourth person charged over alleged
OL,4,Carson attack in Golders Green
OL,6,FA fourth person charged after four
OL,7,FJewish community ambulances were
OL,8,Ftorched in north-west London is
OL,9,Fexpected to appear in court on
OL,10,FSaturday.
OL,12,F18 year old Judex Atshani from
OL,13,FDagenham has been charged with one
OL,14,Fcount of arson with intent to damage
OL,15,Fproperty and being reckless as to
OL,16,Fwhether life would be endangered, the
OL,17,FCrown Prosecution Service said.
OL,19,FHe is in custody and expected to
OL,20,Fappear at Westminster Magistrates'
OL,21,FCourt on Saturday.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/5
