CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776682974
OL,3,CFourth person charged over alleged
OL,4,Carson attack in Golders Green
OL,6,FThe ambulances from Hatzola, a
OL,7,Fvolunteer-led ambulance service
OL,8,Foperating in the Golders Green area,
OL,9,Fwere set on fire in the early hours of
OL,10,FMarch 23, causing gas canisters stored
OL,11,Fin the vehicles to explode.
OL,13,FIt caused #1 million worth of damage,
OL,14,Fthe court has previously heard.
OL,16,FJudex Atshatshi was arrested on April
OL,17,F16 after counter terrorism detectives
OL,18,Fattended two addresses in east London,
OL,19,Fthe Metropolitan Police said.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/5
