PN,40703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776682974
OL,3,CFourth person charged over alleged
OL,4,Carson attack in Golders Green
OL,6,FAnother 18-year-old arrested on the
OL,7,Fsame day on suspicion of conspiracy to
OL,8,Fcommit arson with intent to endanger
OL,9,Flife has been released on bail until a
OL,10,Fdate in July.
OL,12,FTwo British men, Hamza Iqbal and Rehan
OL,13,FKhan from Leyton and a 17-year-old boy
OL,14,Ffrom Walthamstow, are each charged
OL,15,Fwith one count of arson being reckless
OL,16,Fas to whether life would be
OL,17,Fendangered. They were remanded in
OL,18,Fcustody earlier this month.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/5
