OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776682974
OL,3,CFourth person charged over alleged
OL,4,Carson attack in Golders Green
OL,6,FFrank Ferguson, head of the Crown
OL,7,FProsecution Service's special crime
OL,8,Fand counter terrorism division, said:
OL,10,F"We have worked closely with the
OL,11,FMetropolitan Police's Counter
OL,12,FTerrorism Command as it carried out
OL,13,Fits investigation.
OL,15,F"We remind all concerned that criminal
OL,16,Fproceedings against these defendants
OL,17,Fare active and that they have the
OL,18,Fright to a fair trial.
